<h2 id="fsInf">What is FoodSaver?</h2>
<h2 id="info"> FoodSaver is a free service designed to help families keep track of the food they have so that they can save money and food.
    FoodSaver will: </h2>


<h2 id="info2">
    Help families keep track of what food they already have even if it is is hidden in the depths of their fridge. <br> </br>
    Send reminders to eat food before it begins to go bad.<br> </br>
    Suggest recipies for new meals made from the excess food in their pantry. </h2>

